OL,3,C'Real first lady of jazz' Adelaide
OL,4,CHall to be honoured with blue plaque
OL,6,FMusician and dancer Adelaide Hall `
OL,7,Fhailed as the "real first lady of
OL,8,Fjazz" ` is to be honoured with a blue
OL,9,Fplaque at her London home.
OL,11,FThe scat pioneer, who was born in
OL,12,FBrooklyn, New York, spent 55 years in
OL,13,FLondon and an English Heritage plaque
OL,14,Fwill be unveiled at 1 Collingham Road
OL,15,Fin Kensington, which was her home for
OL,16,F27 years.
OL,18,FShe died in the capital in 1993 at the
OL,19,Fage of 92.
