OL,6,FShe told an told an interviewer in
OL,7,FJune 1980: "I do like London very
OL,8,Fmuch. I like it because it's quiet `
OL,9,Fand I like the quiet life."
OL,11,FHall was a pioneer of "scat" singing,
OL,12,Frenowned for using her voice as a pure
OL,13,Fjazz instrument.
OL,15,FShe is believed to have had the
OL,16,Flongest recording career of any 20th-
OL,17,Fcentury artist and was recognised by
OL,18,FGuinness World Records in 2003 for
OL,19,Freleasing material over eight
OL,20,Fconsecutive decades.
