OL,6,FStephen Bourne, historian and author
OL,7,Fof Sophisticated Lady ` A Celebration
OL,8,FOf Adelaide Hall, said: "Adelaide was
OL,9,Fa rarity in showbiz, because she
OL,10,Fhonestly never had a bad word to say
OL,11,Fabout anyone.
OL,13,F"She was so versatile and took so many
OL,14,Fartistic risks, but when I think of
OL,15,Fher it will always be as the real
OL,16,Ffirst lady of jazz, admired by the
OL,17,Flikes of Ella Fitzgerald and Elisabeth
OL,18,FWelch.
