OL,6,F"Having known her, I don't doubt that
OL,7,Fshe would be absolutely thrilled to
OL,8,Fbits to get a blue plaque. I'm sure
OL,9,Fshe is smiling wherever she is."
OL,11,FMusician YolanDa Brown, who is a
OL,12,Fmember of the blue plaques panel,
OL,13,Fsaid: "Adelaide Hall's music was
OL,14,Funlike anything that people had heard
OL,15,Fbefore.
