OL,3,C'Real first lady of jazz' Adelaide
OL,4,CHall to be honoured with blue plaque
OL,6,F"She could do it all of course `
OL,7,Fshowtunes, gospel and music hall
OL,8,Fsongs. But it was this voice, wordless
OL,9,Fsinging bursting out of her like it
OL,10,Fwas the most natural thing in the
OL,11,Fworld, that really set her apart.
OL,13,F"I am delighted that English Heritage
OL,14,Fare recognising her exceptional talent
OL,15,Fwith a blue plaque."
OL,17,FBrown told the PA news agency: "The
OL,18,Fblue plaques are about people who have
OL,19,Freally contributed to our heritage and
OL,20,Fcontributed to London.
