OL,6,F"She's got this global appeal, coming
OL,7,Ffrom America, and musically people are
OL,8,Freferencing her in their music and
OL,9,Fsometimes they don't even know that
OL,10,Fthey are.
OL,12,F"If they heard Duke Ellington's Creole
OL,13,FLove Call, just hearing her scatting
OL,14,Fon that song, through to all of the
