OL,3,C'Real first lady of jazz' Adelaide
OL,4,CHall to be honoured with blue plaque
OL,6,F"I think, you know, somebody with that
OL,7,Fmuch impact could easily go under the
OL,8,Fradar after many generations passed,
OL,9,Fso it's really nice that a blue plaque
OL,10,Fcan commemorate her and help people on
OL,11,Ftheir journey as they go on to
OL,12,Fdiscover her more."
OL,14,FHall moved to the upper part of 1
OL,15,FCollingham Road, an imposing 1870s
OL,16,Fcorner house, in Kensington, on July
OL,17,F21 1952, according to rate books.
